      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. It's a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance tasks.",
