    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute gem and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, so it\u2019s in incredible shape inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure. I'm really looking for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
