    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom state, featuring supple, uncreased leather and a cabin that still smells like the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine runs with surgical precision, supported by a comprehensive folder of documented service records and original manuals. Every button, dial, and sensor functions perfectly, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been pampered since mile one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
