    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every facet, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been meticulously curated to meet the highest standards. Mechanically sound and aesthetically indistinguishable from a new model, this offering is tailored for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and peak performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
