    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered like a member of the family. It seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It's a total dream to drive and is ready for a brand new home. I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to take this home next\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
